    {
        "content": "<p>cfallin <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/issues/1125#issuecomment-4510982332\">commented</a> on <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/issues/1125\">issue #1125</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>We're doing old-issue triage. It looks like we now have block status tracked in <code>cranelift-frontend</code> and we <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/blob/dc740c90998192dac899df0034a3696861f29f5d/cranelift/frontend/src/frontend.rs#L1189-L1198\">set status to partial (not empty) only when instructions have been added</a>. So I'll go ahead and close this issue. Thanks!</p>\n</blockquote>",
